.TH vdf_get_ull 3

.SH NAME
vdf_get_ull

.SH LIBRARY
Valve Data Format Parser Library (libvdfc)

.SH SYNOPSIS
#include <vdfc/vdf.h>

unsigned long long vdf_get_ull(const VDFNode *object, const char *key, unsigned long long fallback);

.SH DESCRIPTION
Look up a direct child of `object` by key and return its `unsigned long long` value.

If the child is not found or is not a valid integer string, returns `fallback`.

.SH RETURN VALUE
Returns the child's `unsigned long long` value, or `fallback`.

.SH ERRORS
None.

